{EAST cannot rebid the 5-card \S suit, cannot support WEST's \Ds, 
and cannot bid Notrump without a \H stopper.

So she bids 3\C, New Minor Forcing, asking WEST to describe his hand further.

WEST doesn't have three \Ss, nor does he have four \Hs. 
But he does have \Hs stopped, so bids 2NT. East is not strong 
enough to bid game so she passes.}

